  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">Although petitioners&#x27; intention was to<BR ALIGN='left'/>dispose of the chemical manufacturing<BR ALIGN='left'/>business eventually, the fact that a<BR ALIGN='left'/>going business was transferred and<BR ALIGN='left'/>operated left the new company and<BR ALIGN='left'/>petitioners, its shareholders, in a<BR ALIGN='left'/>position where they stood to gain or<BR ALIGN='left'/>lose from operations just as before the<BR ALIGN='left'/>transfer; if business conditions<BR ALIGN='left'/>warranted it, the business could have<BR ALIGN='left'/>been continued indefinitely.</TD></TR>
